skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my pie
des:
Ask Alexa to figure out what kind of pie you are. She will ask you some questions to narrow it down. Once she tells you what flavor of pie you are, you can ask her to tell you more about your personality. 

Have fun!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
